Add @whole peeled tomatoes{400%g} to a bowl and crush them by hand, squeezing them through your fingers. -- If the tomatoes are really watery after crushing them, let them drain in a strainer before moving on.

Add @salt{0.5%tsp}, @garlic{1%clove}(minced), and @fresh basil{8%leaves} torn by hand.

Let the sauce sit for at least ~{15%minutes} to allow the flavors to develop.
